<aside
  id="info-panel"
  class="glass-panel fixed inset-y-6 right-6 z-20 hidden w-[min(360px,calc(100vw-3rem))] flex-col overflow-hidden p-6 md:p-8"
>
  <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
    <div class="flex min-w-0 items-center gap-3">
      <span
        id="info-panel-tag"
        class="truncate rounded-full border border-[var(--accent-cyan)]/30 bg-[var(--accent-cyan)]/12 px-2 py-1 text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-300"
      >
        NODE_EXTRACTED
      </span>
      <span
        id="info-panel-meta"
        class="hidden text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500 md:inline"
      >
        COORD // --
      </span>
    </div>

    <button
      id="info-panel-close"
      type="button"
      class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400 transition-colors hover:border-[var(--accent-orange)]/40 hover:text-[var(--accent-orange)]"
    >
      关闭
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="overflow-y-auto pr-1">
    <h2 id="info-panel-title" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      加载中...
    </h2>
    <p id="info-panel-subtitle" class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
      星系档案正在同步，等待场景控制器写入当前焦点数据。
    </p>

    <div
      id="info-panel-content"
      class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300"
    >
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/25 p-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500">
          Status
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
          点击恒星或行星后，这里会显示当前目标的摘要、统计信息和文章列表。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>
